
You are known for having a bad temper and yes things with you can get heated pretty quickly. The things is, you don't like drawing attention to yourself so you might get calmer if that light is beaming on you. When upset, you are usually angrier with yourself for showing weakness. This is a problem for you because you want to always show that you're in control. Its okay Scorpio, anger is actually a healthy emotion when not blown out of proportion.